==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Doss house
<hw>Doss house</hw>. <def>A cheap lodging house.</def></p>

<p><q>They [street Arabs] consort together and sleep in low <qex>doss
houses</qex> where they meet with all kinds of villainy.</q> <rj><qau>W.
Besant.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dossel</ent>⟦br⟧
